    {
      "id": "standard_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "standard_0",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition. It shows moderate wear on the interior and exterior, including some scratches and minor dents. The mechanical systems are functional, though the car may require maintenance in the near future.",
      "price": 20000.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "fair",
      "quality_value": 0.4,
      "timestep_posted": 40
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in truly impeccable, showroom-quality condition. The exterior paint is flawless with a deep, mirror-like finish and absolutely no scratches, dings, or imperfections. Inside, the cabin remains in pristine state, with the leather upholstery and trim showing no signs of wear, and all electronic features functioning perfectly. Mechanically, the car is sound and drives like it just rolled off the assembly line, having been meticulously maintained and garage-kept. This is a rare find for a buyer seeking a vehicle that looks and performs as if it were brand new.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "mint",
      "quality_value": 1.0,
      "timestep_posted": 40
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting an automotive specimen of unparalleled caliber. This vehicle remains in a state of preservation indistinguishable from its original showroom delivery. Every surface, from the factory-spec mechanical assemblies to the immaculate interior appointments, reflects an uncompromising standard of stewardship. This is a definitive acquisition for the discerning collector who demands excellence without exception. Impeccably maintained and offered in pristine condition.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 40
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\udc4b If you've been looking for a ride that feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor, you have found it! This beauty has been my absolute pride and joy, and I have babied it every single day. It is in truly pristine condition\u2014not a scratch or a smudge in sight! It drives like a dream and still has that fresh, new-car feel. I\u2019m honestly a little sad to see it go, but I know it\u2019s going to make its next owner so happy. Come take a look and see for yourself; you won\u2019t be disappointed! \u2728",
      "price": 43500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 40
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_14_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_14",
      "description": "Offered is a superlative 2002 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six power plant. This collector-grade example boasts a precision-calibrated dual-VANOS system and recently replaced VAC-coated rod bearings, ensuring mechanical longevity. The chassis integrity is bolstered by proactive subframe reinforcement using Turner Motorsport plates. Power is delivered through a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox to a factory variable M-differential lock, providing exceptional lateral grip and corner-exit traction. The suspension geometry is maintained by a Bilstein PSS10 adjustable coilover system, offering superior damping control over the original Sachs units. The exterior retains its original factory luster with zero panel gap deviations, while the interior remains a time capsule of Nappa leather and intact soft-touch plastics. A truly turnkey performance icon for the purist.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 40
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_17_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_17",
      "description": "2021 sedan. Mint condition. Single owner. Always garaged. No cosmetic or mechanical flaws. Full service history available.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 40
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_18_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_18",
      "description": "This vehicle is a true collector's dream, preserved in showroom condition since day one. The exterior boasts a deep, mirror-like finish with absolutely no chips, swirls, or scratches, while the interior remains pristine with supple, wear-free leather and untouched trim. Meticulously maintained, it has been stored in a climate-controlled garage and serviced exclusively by certified specialists ahead of every scheduled interval. With exceptionally low mileage and a flawless mechanical pedigree, it drives with the precision and smoothness of a brand-new car. Included are all original keys, manuals, and a comprehensive binder of maintenance records.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 40
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "We are proud to present this exemplary vehicle, currently held in showroom condition. This specimen represents a rare opportunity for the discerning buyer, exhibiting impeccable aesthetic integrity and flawless mechanical performance. Meticulously maintained and preserved with the utmost care, the vehicle remains indistinguishable from its original state. This is an investment-grade acquisition for those who demand nothing less than perfection.",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 40
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_15_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_15",
      "description": "Hey there! You have seriously got to see this beauty in person. It is in absolutely stunning shape\u2014honestly, it looks and drives like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I've babied this car since day one, and it really shows in every little detail. If you're looking for that 'new car' feel without the 'new car' price tag, this is definitely the one for you. Drop me a message and come take it for a spin!",
      "price": 44900.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 40
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_16_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_16",
      "description": "Presenting a concours-level example of mid-engine precision. This specimen features a perfectly balanced chassis paired with a turbocharged 2.5L flat-four powerplant, delivering linear torque across the entire rev range. Equipped with Porsche Active Suspension Management (PASM) and a mechanical limited-slip differential, the handling dynamics are razor-sharp. The short-throw six-speed manual transmission offers tactile gear engagement and rev-matching capability, while the factory-spec sport exhaust provides an evocative acoustic profile. Meticulously maintained with zero bolster wear and a flawless undercarriage, this vehicle retains its factory-fresh structural rigidity and aesthetic brilliance. A true driver's car in peerless mechanical and cosmetic form.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 40
    },
    {
